MARKETEER v0.1.1
----------------
A trading-bot project written in python.

SUPPORTED MARKETS
-----------------
Monitoring only: Bullion Vault (http://www.bullionvault.com/)

BACKLOG
-------
https://trello.com/board/marketeer/50369a0c3a5753ff20071050

USAGE
-----
Run testscript.py to see live data from the Bullion Vault London Gold
GBP market. The script calls the Bullion Vault public API twice, waiting 30s
between each call, and displays the current bid price, offer price, and spread
each time.

